text: Juila Goulding (born 27 March 1985) is an English actress. Since 2016, she has played Shona Ramsey on the long-running ITV soap opera Coronation Street. She was born in Greater Manchester, England, United Kingdom. == Other websites == * Category:1985 births Category:Living people Category:English stage actors Category:English television actors Category:Actors from Greater Manchester
